data.title: RC Praga Prague
data.meta_description: Welcome to official website of RC Praga Prague - the most successful club in Czech rugby history!
data.text:
Rugby is a great way to stay in shape, meet new people and enjoy loads of fun. This is something that holds all over the world and we are proud to be a part of the global rugby community. If you miss rugby, we hope that our field is for you the right place to go! For the overview of the events of our club, please see the Calendar.

If you are looking for a club in Prague to play rugby, you are very welcomed at our field.

We have two squads in senior category (1st XV and 2nd XV), so it doesn't matter whether you want to try rugby or continue on competetive level.

All you need to do is just visit one of our training sessions, that take place usually on Tuesdays and Thursdays from 6.30 pm. For the current training schedule, please check our Calendar or contact us via the form below.

Prague is a beautiful city, home of vibrant nightlife and excelent while cheap beer. If you are looking for the right place for you tour, you have just found it!

If there is a free weekend within our match schedule, we are happy to have a friendly match and a beer with you. We have experience with organizing third half at our clubhouse.
